<TEXT>
tiananmen square a raucous rallying point for 
students demanding democratic rights by day at night becomes a 
carnival ground of concerts dancing and exotic food 
while thousands of students camped out on the square doze in 
rickety huts night owls sing folk songs and dance to tinny sounds 
