that west germans see a historic chance to overcome the tensions 
between east and west 
but making clear which side of the european divide west germany 
stands on kohl assured bush we will never allow our commitment 
to the alliance to waver our future does not lie somewhere in no 
mans land between east and west our future lies in the community 
of free peoples 
kohls conservative christian democratic party has recently 
suffered in opinion polls and regional elections because of a 
general drift to the left among voters his popularity sunk to a 
dangerous low during the missile dispute when he appeared to take 
the stand against nato in response to public pressure 
