whose siren song lured sailors to shipwreck and death 
the waterway path through the rhines deeplycut valley is one 
of germanys most popular tourist attractions followed by millions 
each year 
the path is lined with picturesque castles and carefully tended 
vineyards clinging to the hillsides 
tourists pay about 17 for a trip as long as bushs but they 
dont get the same vip attention 
