destroyed a combined 1269 nuclear missiles during the first year 
of the intermediaterange nuclear forces treaty the us officials 
said wednesday 
the two sides also have conducted a combined 340 inspections to 
verify the missile destruction and ensure compliance with other 
terms of the treaty 
