philip morris cos is testmarketing a new 
virtually nicotinefree cigarette that the company believes has as 
much flavor as regular cigarettes 
published reports said philip morris was testing the cigarette 
but the company refused to confirm or deny the reports wednesday 
saying it does not comment on product testing 
however a source who asked not to be identified said the 
reports were correct 
the lower nicotine levels in the new cigarette which will be 
sold under the names merit free and next from merit are achieved 
through a process similar to the decaffeination of coffee 
the cigarettes competitors which include american brands 
incs carlton and rjr nabisco incs now use a different 
technology that affects the taste of the tobacco 
the new cigarette will contain 01 milligram of nicotine the 
same amount as in carlton and now 
lownicotine cigarettes appeal to smokers who are trying to cut 
down their intake of harmful substances contained in tobacco smoke 
the prospect of a new potentially successful product apparently 
appealed to investors wednesday philip morris stock rose 112 a 
share to close at 13912 in new york stock exchange composite 
trading 
