if tyson foods inc is so eager to buy the 
holly farms corp it should simply raise its 11 billion offer a 
lawyer for a competing bidder told a chancery court judge wednesday 
in delaware 
why doesnt tyson open its pocketbook said franklin 
balotti a lawyer representing conagra inc of omaha neb 
