farms holly lawyer kenneth nachbar said tyson and conagra were 
dealing behind the scenes until shortly before the proposed merger 
was announced 
tyson offered to pay conagra 50 million to step aside but an 
agreement based on that offer fell apart at the last minute 
nachbar said 
